title: Hour 3 - Peter Schrager, David Spade
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Peter Schrager, David Spade
description:
Dan talks to Peter Schrager about NFL Commissioner Roger Goodell's comments regarding the Pro Bowl. And Actor, Writer, Comedian, David Spade stops by to share some Hollywood stories and lament the failure of his Phoenix Suns.
